NAME

    Dancer2::Session::CGISession - Share Dancer Session with CGI::Session

SYNOPSIS

      use Dancer2::Session::CGISession;

DESCRIPTION

    Dancer2::Session::CGISession is a session engine for Dancer2 to
    interact with CGI::Session; Mostly usefull if you need to share
    sessions created by non-Dancer apps which are already using
    CGI::Session. That Plugin is heavily inspired from
    Dancer::Session::CGISession

    This module is a work in progress

    You can set CGI::Session drivers and parameters using Dancer2
    configuration

        session: "CGISession"
    
        engines:
          session:
            CGISession:
              driver: "driver:file:
              driver_params:
                "Directory": "/tmp
              name: "session name"

